{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01N49sg653b34xqMMD2V3Foi","type":"tool_result","content":"   275→  <step n=\"5\" goal=\"Create comprehensive story file\">\n   276→    <critical>📝 CREATE ULTIMATE STORY FILE - The developer's master implementation guide!</critical>\n   277→\n   278→    <action>Initialize from template.md:\n   279→    {default_output_file}</action>\n   280→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">story_header</template-output>\n   281→\n   282→    <!-- Story foundation from epics analysis -->\n   283→    <template-output\n   284→      file=\"{default_output_file}\">story_requirements</template-output>\n   285→\n   286→    <!-- FINAL AC QUALITY CHECK before writing the rest of the story -->\n   287→    <critical>🔍 AC QUALITY GATE — Review ACs before finalizing the story file</critical>\n   288→    <action>Before proceeding, review every AC in the story file:\n   289→      1. Does each AC describe observable user-facing behavior (not just code artifacts)?\n   290→         - REJECT: \"function X exists\", \"module exports Y\", \"returns RendererHandle\"\n   291→         - ACCEPT: \"operator sees X in the terminal\", \"command outputs Y\", \"dashboard displays Z\"\n   292→      2. Is every behavioral requirement from the UX spec and PRD (within this story's scope) covered by at least one AC?\n   293→         - If not, add the missing AC now\n   294→      3. Are ACs balanced — specific enough to verify but not so narrow they miss the spirit of the requirement?\n   295→         - A single AC like \"header shows story key\" is too narrow if the spec says \"header shows story key, phase, elapsed time, and progress\"\n   296→         - Combine related display elements into one AC that covers the full expected output\n   297→      4. Can each AC be verified by running the system and observing output (not just reading source code)?\n   298→    </action>\n   299→\n   300→    <!-- Developer context section - MOST IMPORTANT PART -->\n   301→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">\n   302→    developer_context_section</template-output> **DEV AGENT GUARDRAILS:** <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">\n   303→    technical_requirements</template-output>\n   304→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">architecture_compliance</template-output>\n   305→    <template-output\n   306→      file=\"{default_output_file}\">library_framework_requirements</template-output>\n   307→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">\n   308→    file_structure_requirements</template-output>\n   309→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">testing_requirements</template-output>\n   310→\n   311→    <!-- Previous story intelligence -->\n   312→    <check\n   313→      if=\"previous story learnings available\">\n   314→      <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">previous_story_intelligence</template-output>\n   315→    </check>\n   316→\n   317→    <!-- Git intelligence -->\n   318→    <check\n   319→      if=\"git analysis completed\">\n   320→      <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">git_intelligence_summary</template-output>\n   321→    </check>\n   322→\n   323→    <!-- Latest technical specifics -->\n   324→    <check if=\"web research completed\">\n   325→      <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">latest_tech_information</template-output>\n   326→    </check>\n   327→\n   328→    <!-- Project context reference -->\n   329→    <template-output\n   330→      file=\"{default_output_file}\">project_context_reference</template-output>\n   331→\n   332→    <!-- Final status update -->\n   333→    <template-output file=\"{default_output_file}\">\n   334→    story_completion_status</template-output>\n   335→\n   336→    <!-- CRITICAL: Set status to ready-for-dev -->\n   337→    <action>Set story Status to: \"ready-for-dev\"</action>\n   338→    <action>Add completion note: \"Ultimate\n   339→    context engine analysis completed - comprehensive developer guide created\"</action>"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_017LihutVV2SfFnAxcKajyK2","session_id":"c452ddd6-f9a0-4cb1-9871-4264c6441698","uuid":"a461d814-7327-4224-9e8a-c4e1ac5d7df2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T12:39:47.277Z"}
